name: Washed Up (itch) (UF Digital Worlds Institute)
description:
Washed Up

Created by Duo Interactive

  • Odeyls Valdes-Santiago
  • Vivianne Everington

A newly hatched tortoise, helpful hermit crabs, deadly saltwater crabs, seagulls, broken bottles and other trash across several levels until you are reunited with your family.

An epic adventure in a watercolor hand-painted world so beautiful you have to see it.

Who would not want to experience the beach journey Duo Interactive have created for us. Download and start your crawl now.
